  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK262">
<l>tavamun tavamuṭaiyārk kāku mavamataṉai</l>
<l> yaḵtilār mēṟkoḷ vatu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Austerities can only be borne, and their benefits enjoyed, by those who have practised them (in a former birth); it will be useless for those who have not done so, to attempt to practise them (now).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
